## ğŸ“ Dataset Columns
The dataset includes detailed sales records with the following columns:

- `Order Number`
- `Quantity Ordered`
- `Price Each`
- `Order Line Number`
- `Sales`
- `Order Date`
- `Month_ID`
- `Year_ID`
- `Product Line`
- `MSRP`
